  "body": "There could be more cases, but an obvious one: when i want to edit a link in a text box, removing `/` replaces the `:/ ` with emoji, which is unwanted in this case. I think we need to make suggestions for such replacements and allow user to decide wether he needs it or not\r\n\r\n**To reproduce:**\r\n\r\n1. open any chat\r\n2. paste a link to the chat box\r\n3. try to remove `/`\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/82375995/129055813-5a72ebbf-b608-4f63-a75d-e945d7ebf18a.mov\r\n\r\n",
